unittitle_ssm: Wesley L. Baker manuscript on Thomas Osman
abstract_ssm: A typewritten manuscript by Wesley L. Baker on Thomas Osman and the early history of his settlement at Hashamomuck Neck in present-day Southold, Long Island, N.Y. Thomas Osman was born in England in 1621 and established a settlement at Hashamomuck Neck around 1637 or 1638. The manuscript covers the period circa 1637 to 1700.
